Both characters aren't all-powerful and have major faults that are elaborated on for multiple chapters, and both stories hook us with the anthros and gives us a reason WHY the anthros are in the universe, AND both do so almost immediately (I'm talking, prologue or chapter one, here; not "I'm building up to it with six chapters of murder).
